race.comment: ALL IN KNOTS (7) recorded a 2.25 lengths win (22.51) in a Novice race last time at this track. Looks suited here and rates on top. ENTERTAINING (2) has an excellent record over this course and distance having never missed the placings in four starts, including three wins. Placed last time (22.57) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing second and beaten a nose. Looks one of the chances. FLETCHER KEEPING (1) pinged the lids and led throughout to score last start (22.62) at this track in Grade 6 over 400m. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Leading chance again. MAN ABOUT TOWN (5) is a course and distance winner with definite claims.
